deleteSelectedFromFPlan(25.10)                  deleteSelectedFromFPlan(25.10)

Name
       deleteSelectedFromFPlan  - Deletes the currently selected floorplan ob-
       jects

Syntax
        deleteSelectedFromFPlan

       [-help]

       Deletes the currently selected floorplan objects. You can use this com-
       mand at any point in the design flow.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the deleteSelectedFromFPlan  com-
              mand.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteSelectedFromFPlan

Related Information
              * deleteAllFPObjects

              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

